{"type": "article", "id": 27725, "title": "扶手椅与茶几组合", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-03T06:59:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702123006TUchLCAnfM0DbzvS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>蓝色的天空（ten）与白色的大地（ci），这个扶手椅和茶几的组合由日本设计师 <a href=\"http://www.naotofukasawa.com/\">Naoto Fukasawa</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.driade.com/en/\">Draide</a> 所设计。扶手椅 ten 的靠背微微倾斜，表面的材质还有织布和皮革两种可选。与此呼应的茶几 ci 的桌面由白色大理石制成，纹理使人联想到大地的表面。虽然都是冷色调，但它们的底部都依靠深色的木腿支撑，增添了几分暖色。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123003MBcQWAdv3N9Uoz1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.47066015\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021230042KHLSVTagsuMkNY0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021230040mxC41RIPQDUfioF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702123005rN2zWtlTgomO98HX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99022005\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}